data.description:
Beautiful brick ranch-4BR 2.5BA in highly sought after Murray Hill neighborhood. Home features large front porch, foyer, formal LR/Flex Room & Formal Dining Room with 9' ceilings. Updated kitchen is roomy with island, dbl ovens, 42" cabinets & granite tops. Laundry Rm with half bath conveniently located near the door to garage. Great room with fireplace, built-ins w/storage. Spacious Master BR, WIC, Master Bath has dual vanities & separate shower. Updated hall bath & 3 other nice size bedrooms round out the home. HVAC system including new ducts in 2018 & roof in 2012 per the previous seller. Very nice mature landscaping. Rear patio to sit and enjoy the large backyard. Come take a look at this beautiful gem!!

**BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER**
